Segmenting foods on a dinner plate
Developed an Win32 Application which can load image and in which the user segments the food items by using the below options -
a) left-click to draw a contour around a food item that will automatically shrinks to wrap to
the food boundary.
b)right-click a point within a food item that will automatically
grow a contour to its outer boundary.
c)shift-click to manually drag a contour point to a new location.
Segmentation was achieved using Rubber Band , Balloon and Neutral Size Active Contour Models.
